{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/star-wars-day-may-4th/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"May the 4th Be with You! Ini Dia Sejarah Star Wars Day!","content":"<p>Setiap tahunnya, tanggal 4 Mei selalu dikenang oleh para fans Star Wars. Biasanya, hari ini disebut sebagai Star Wars Day. Sepanjang hari selama tanggal 4 Mei, para fans merayakan segala hal berbau Star Wars dan mengenang apa saja yang membuat mereka mencintai serial <em>space opera</em> ciptaan George Lucas ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46763\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46763\" data-attachment-id=\"46763\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/star-wars-day-may-4th/attachment/01-star-wars-day/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-star-wars-day.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-star-wars-day\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-star-wars-day.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46763\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-star-wars-day.jpg\" alt=\"01 star wars day\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-star-wars-day.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46763\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: WampaDude</p></div></p>\n<p>Apa yang mendasari terpilihnya tanggal 4 Mei sebagai Star Wars Day? Alasan utamanya karena tanggal 4 Mei bisa dibaca sebagai plesetan salah satu kalimat bersejarah dalam Star Wars. <em>“May the Force be with you,” </em>bisa dibaca menjadi <em>“May the 4<sup>th</sup> be with you,”</em> dimana bagian <em>“May the 4<sup>th</sup>”</em> (dibaya May the Fourth) merujuk ke tanggal 4 Mei. Sejauh ini sudah paham?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46764\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46764\" data-attachment-id=\"46764\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/star-wars-day-may-4th/attachment/02-star-wars-day/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-star-wars-day.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-star-wars-day\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-star-wars-day.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46764\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-star-wars-day.jpg\" alt=\"02-star-wars-day\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-star-wars-day.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46764\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: La Chicchara</p></div></p>\n<p>Namun, sejarah Star Wars Day lebih dari sekedar main plesetan kata. Kalimat plesetan tersebut pertama kali muncul di tahun 1979, 2 tahun setelah Star Wars tayang di bioskop. Partai Konservatif di Inggris membeli sebuah kolom iklan di koran The London Evening News, untuk merayakan kemenangan Margaret Thatcher sebagai perdana menteri Inggris yang baru. Iklan tersebut menampilkan tulisan <em>&#8220;May the Fourth Be with You, Maggie. Congratulations.&#8221;</em></p>\n<p>Kalimat tersebut kemudian digunakan lagi dalam sebuah depat parliament Inggris di tahun 1994, dan dalam buku The Science of Star Wars karangan Jeanne Cavelos pada tahun 1999.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46765\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46765\" data-attachment-id=\"46765\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/star-wars-day-may-4th/attachment/03-star-wars-day/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-star-wars-day.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-star-wars-day\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-star-wars-day.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46765\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-star-wars-day.jpg\" alt=\"03-star-wars-day\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-star-wars-day.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46765\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Facebook</p></div></p>\n<p>Kalimat <em>“May the 4<sup>th</sup> be with you”</em> dalam era media sosial pertama kali mencuat pada tahun 2008. Sebuah grup Facebook didirikan dengan nama <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/16743711387/\">Luke Skywalker Day: May the 4<sup>th</sup></a>. Grup ini dibentuk untuk mengenang karakter Luke Skywalker pada tanggal 4 Mei. Walaupun grup tersebut tak menciptakan sensasi viral, popularitasnya menyebar di kalangan mahasiswa, dan secara sporadis mereka membentuk perayaan Star Wars Day mereka sendiri.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46766\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46766\" data-attachment-id=\"46766\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/star-wars-day-may-4th/attachment/04-star-wars-day/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-star-wars-day.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-star-wars-day\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-star-wars-day.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46766\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-star-wars-day.jpg\" alt=\"04-star-wars-day\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-star-wars-day.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46766\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Philippine Star</p></div></p>\n<p>Setelah berbagai acara Star Wars Day diselenggarakan secara swadaya setiap tanggal 4 Mei, baru pada tahun 2011-lah dibuat acara Star Wars Day dengan skala yang lebih besar. Star Wars Day resmi pertama kali diadakan pada 4 Mei 2011 di Ontario, Kanada. Acara ini menampilkan kontes game show trivia <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trilogi-asli-star-wars-lebih-baik-dari-trilogi-prequel-nya-yakin/\">trilogi original</a> Star Wars, kontes <em>cosplay</em>, serta <em>screening</em> film dan klip pendek.</p>\n<p>Semenjak Lucasarts dibeli oleh Disney, taipan hiburan raksasa itu juga turut merayakan 4 Mei sebagai Star Wars Day. Berbagai perayaan Star Wars diselenggarakan di Disneyland dan Walt Disney World seluruh dunia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46767\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46767\" data-attachment-id=\"46767\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/star-wars-day-may-4th/attachment/05-star-wars-day/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-star-wars-day.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-star-wars-day\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-star-wars-day.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46767\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-star-wars-day.jpg\" alt=\"05-star-wars-day\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-star-wars-day.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-star-wars-day-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46767\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Inside The Magic</p></div></p>\n<p>Tahun ini pun berbagai event Star Wars Day diadakan di seluruh dunia; baik dalam tingkat daerah maupun tingkat internasional. Bagaimana, kamu tertarik untuk ikut perayaan Star Wars Day? Tak perlu memaksakan diri untuk pergi ke event luar kota. Maraton film Star Wars di rumah pun sudah cukup untuk merayakan Star Wars Day. Apapun yang kamu lakukan, jangan lupa<em>, “May the 4<sup>th</sup> be with you!”</em></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"a374585b-8342-5fb6-b0ab-b335da04f2ea"}}}